**Government Tender Announcement**

**Procurement Title:** One (1) Senior Procurement Specialist
**Procurement Number:** cb-675-90173765
**Solicitation Number:** W8486-249611/A
**Tender Closing Date:** June 4, 2024, 2:00 PM EDT

The Department of National Defence invites interested Pre-Qualified Suppliers to participate in a Request for Proposal (RFP) for the services of a Senior Procurement Specialist. The requirement is to establish one (1) contract for an initial period of three (3) years, with two (2) one-year optional extension periods.

**Objective:**
This RFP seeks to engage a Pre-Qualified Supplier who can provide professional procurement services to support the Department's project management initiatives. The selected Supplier will be responsible for providing procurement support services that meet the Department's requirements under the Treasury Board policies and directives.

**Eligibility:**
This solicitation is open to the following Pre-Qualified Suppliers under the Task and Solutions Professional Services (TSPS) Supply Arrangement (SA) number E60ZT-18TSPS:

[List of 80 Pre-Qualified Suppliers]

**Briefing Material:**
RFP documents will be e-mailed directly to Qualified Pre-Qualified Suppliers who are being invited to bid on this requirement. Bidders are advised that the RFP documents are not available on the CanadaBuys Tender Management Application website.

**Security Clearance:**
Supplier Security Clearance required: Secret
Security Level required (Document Safeguarding): None
FOCI Review: None

**Location of Work:**
Region: National Capital Region
Specific Location: 45 Sacré-Cœur, Gatineau, Quebec

**Contact Information:**
For any inquiries regarding this RFP, please contact:
Jennifer Ouellet, Contracting Authority
Jennifer.ouellet2@forces.gc.ca, (343) 598-1547

**Note:**
The Crown retains the right to negotiate with Suppliers on any procurement.  
- **sectionEnd** </markdown format applied during the rewrite.?>
